Class ClinicManagerController

java.lang.Object
com.example.javafx_clinicmanager.ClinicManagerController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ClinicManagerController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The Controller class is a management class for the Clinic Manager JavaFX application. It controls all the elements for the software
Author:
Deep Patel, Manan Patel
